                   3: Demos and games for commercial purposes
                  ÍÍÍÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÍÍÍ

    If you find our intros and demos interesting and would like us to make
    something for commercial purposes, do not hesitate to contact us.

    When contacting us, please include a short explanation of the kind of
    production you had in mind. It would help us with the evaluation of
    the size of the project.

    Would you be so kind as to include the following information:

        - What kinds of effects would you be interested in.
        - Should there be any colorful logos, pictures etc.
        - If the demo should have sound, which sound cards
          would you like it to support, and what type of
          music should be played.
        - How big should the demo be in kilobytes and how
          long should the demo be in minutes approximately.
        - Where will the demo be used, and what will it be
          used for.
        - How soon would you like the demo to be finished.
        - Approximately how much would you be willing to
          pay for the demo.

    All our productions are realtime calculations and not animations.
    This means that the speed of the demo depends a lot on the speed
    of the processor, of the video card, and of the sound card.

    You should also bear in mind that we do not make demos for Microsoft
    Windows, or any other GUI operating system. All our productions are
    meant for the IBM PC and compatibles and should be running under
    MS-DOS or PC-DOS.

    You can find our contact information in chapter 8 of this file.


                    4: The distribution and use of our demos
                   ÍÍÍÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÍÍÍ

    All HYPNOSIS productions, except those created for commercial purposes,
    are freeware. You are allowed to copy and distribute them free of charge
    as long as they are distributed unmodified, with their full documentation
    and files. Any copying and/or distributing for money and/or donations is
    strictly prohibited.

    All HYPNOSIS productions cannot be used for commercial purposes without
    written permission of HYPNOSIS. If you are a Public Domain, ShareWare or
    FreeWare distributor, please contact us before adding our products to
    your collection.


